kly into an old-fashioned glass containing ice and 1 oz. of half-and-half. It comes out a milky blue with an orange-like flavor. Exercise caution when working with flaming drinks. Practice pouring from the martini glass using an unflaming mixture so you can do it without spilling. And have a fire extinguisher handy. ALWAYS USE CAUTION WITH FIRE.',1,'\0','\0','\0',NULL),(2754,2,'Hammer','Combine ingredients and serve over ice in a tall glass.',1,'\0','\0','\0',NULL);
